text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Monitoring, helpdesk, threat protection.</p></a></li><li><a role=\"menuitem\" class=\"block px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-cream group transition-colors\" href=\"/services/web-design\"><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[0.85rem] tracking-wide group-hover:text-orange transition-colors mb-0.5\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Local-SEO websites, custom builds, hosted by us.</p></a></li><li><a role=\"menuitem\" class=\"block px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-cream group transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\"><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[0.85rem] tracking-wide group-hover:text-orange transition-colors mb-0.5\">Online Marketing</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Local SEO, Google Ads, GBP management.</p></a></li></ul></div></div></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden w-11 h-11 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\"><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button></nav><div id=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out border-t border-navy/10 max-h-0\"><ul class=\"flex flex-col py-2 px-6 bg-cream\"><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-navy/5\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer\"><span>Services</span><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 \"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out max-h-0\"><ul class=\"pb-3 pl-3 border-l-2 border-orange/30 ml-1\"><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/it-support\">IT Support &amp; Security</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/web-design\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\">Online Marketing</a></li></ul></div></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li class=\"py-4\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary w-full justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></li></ul></div></header><main class=\"font-rajdhani\"><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Web Design &amp; Hosting for Small Business</p><h1 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7 break-words\">A website that<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">earns its keep</span> — and<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-outlined-navy\">stays out of your way.</span></h1><div class=\"lg:hidden flex justify-center mb-8\"><img alt=\"Archie building a website\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[340px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Website.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Website.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Website.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"body-text lg:max-w-[540px] mb-9 text-[1.05rem]\">Fast, professional sites built for local search — with hosting, maintenance, and security handled by the same team that built it. No vendors to juggle. No mystery bills. Just a site that works for your business every day.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary  justify-center sm:justify-start\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-secondary  justify-center sm:justify-start\" href=\"/pricing#web-pricing\">See Pricing<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex justify-end\"><img alt=\"Archie building a website\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[460px] xl:max-w-[520px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Website.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Website.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Website.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>The hard truth</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7\">A bad website doesn&#x27;t just<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">sit there.</span> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">It costs you customers.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text\">Slow loading. Broken on mobile. Hard to find on Google. Old info no one updates. Most small business sites were built once, handed off, and forgotten — leaking trust every day they stay broken.</p></div><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 lg:p-7\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-orange text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-4\">Sound familiar?</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-3.5\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>You wince every time you share your URL</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>It looks broken on a phone</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>Edits cost more than the site is worth</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>Nobody can find you in local search</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg width=\"8\" height=\"8\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 8\" fill=\"currentColor\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></span>You&#x27;re not sure who&#x27;s even hosting it</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-teal-gradient overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container py-16 lg:py-24\"><div class=\"max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-center\"><p class=\"h-section\"><span class=\"text-white\">A site is<!-- --> </span><span class=\"italic text-white\">a tool,</span> <span class=\"text-white\">not an art project.</span><br/><span class=\"text-white\">We build the kind that<!-- --> </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">brings in business.</span></p></div></div></section><section id=\"what-we-do\" class=\"bg-cream scroll-mt-20 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 lg:items-center\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>What we do</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-7\">Fast, professional websites built for<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">local visibility</span> —<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">backed by real support.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text mb-6\">Two paths, depending on what your business needs. Our Local SEO Website ($149/mo) is the fastest way to a credible online presence — clean design, local search baked in, hosted and maintained by us. Our Custom Builds are bespoke, fully owned, and designed around the way your business actually works.</p><p class=\"font-exo font-bold text-navy text-[1rem] leading-[1.65] max-w-[480px]\">Both include hosting, security, and ongoing maintenance. Same team builds it and supports it — no handoffs, no vendors to chase.</p></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 14l4-4\"></path><path d=\"M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 1 16.98 0\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Fast &amp; Performance-Optimized</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">Sites that load fast, score well on Google, and don&#x27;t make visitors wait. Speed is a feature — we treat it like one.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18.37 2.63 14 7l-1-1L8.27 10.73 2 17v5h5l6.27-6.27L18 11l-1-1 4.37-4.37a2.12 2.12 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Designed Around Your Business</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">Not a template dropped on your logo. Clean, modern design that reflects your brand and gives customers a reason to stay.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Built for Local Search</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">Structured to rank when someone nearby searches for what you do. Local SEO foundations baked in from day one.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"2\" y=\"14\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"6.01\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.2rem] lg:text-[1.3rem] tracking-wide mb-2 leading-tight\">Hosting &amp; Maintenance Included</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.65]\">Managed hosting on infrastructure we control, with security, backups, and updates handled. No extra vendor to chase.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between gap-4 mb-10\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>What&#x27;s included</p><h2 class=\"h-compact text-navy\">Every site ships with<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">everything it needs</span> <!-- -->to<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">earn its keep.</span></h2></div><a class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-orange hover:text-navy transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0\" href=\"/pricing#web-pricing\">See pricing tiers <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a></div><ul class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 gap-y-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start font-exo font-medium text-navy/80 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-li